<p><strong>Skills</strong> Perception +4, Stealth +6</p>

<p><strong>Challenge</strong> 1/4 (50 XP)</p>

<p><strong><em>Keen Smell.</em></strong> The panther has advantage on Wisdom (Perception) checks that rely on smell.</p>

<p><strong><em>Pounce.</em></strong> If the panther moves at least 20 ft. straight toward a creature and then hits it with a claw attack on the same turn, that target must succeed on a DC 12 Strength saving throw or be knocked prone. If the target is prone, the panther can make one bite attack against it as a bonus action.</p>

<p><strong>Actions</strong></p>

<p><strong><em>Bite.</em></strong> Melee Weapon Attack: +4 to hit, reach 5 ft., one target. Hit: 5 (1d6 + 2) piercing damage.</p>

<p><strong><em>Claw.</em></strong> Melee Weapon Attack: +4 to hit, reach 5 ft., one target. Hit: 4 (1d4 + 2) slashing damage.</p>

